On Escalation Ticket # 00436293 the new comment has been added: Mara Dobse:

The issue here was the way Slack classifies URLs with http or https with URL tag and not text as for the simple URLs (without http/https mark). The problem has been fixed by searching for the "url" tag if the "text" tag is missing from the request.
A test build containing this fix can be found here: \192.168.14.5Publicgroups_daily_buildsCoSoSys2025-builds2025_04_01EppClient_v6.2.4.0115
@Cristian-Alexandru Halmajan Could you please help with the download link?
Thank you.

[DevOps CommentId:11873967]
